# Armor types

## Helmet
3 armor levels: IIA, IIIA, IIIA+

## Body
4 armor levels: IIIA, IIIA+, III, III+

# Ammo Penetration Color Codes

There are two types of armor with different penetration values for each type: Helmet and armor.

Color codes in photos are represented left to right in the following way:
Helmet I, Helmet IIA, Helmet IIA+, Body IIIA, Body IIIA+, Body III, Body III+

## Color Codes for penetration
Red = no penetration
Orange = low penetration (light bruise/bleed)
Yellow = medium penetration (medium bruise/bleed)
Green = high prenetration (1 Tap/Insta Kill)